node.text:
#PrayForTurkey 🤲🏽 

At least six dead and hundreds homeless after wildfires rage across southern Turkey. Authorities reveal this is due to the change in climate. 

88 wildfires are being contained however at least ten wildfires remain dangerous.

#muslim #islam #turkey

Photo by Muslim on July 31, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Six people are now known to have died in the vast wildfires ravaging southern and western Turkey, authorities said on Saturday. Two firefighters lost their lives as they battled with flames near the town of Manavgat. The tragedy was revealed as ministers said that, while 88 blazes had been brought under control, 10 were still burning dangerously across the landscape.'.
